item.title: How do i make my staff 100k hp
item.dc:creator: @alanpwns alanpwns
item.description:
@alanpwns wrote:

Well,if you go to characters,as if you were going to make them admin or mod,but go down and look at “Character Skills” and it should show their skills, if you change the 99 to 99999 it will be that when they log in. also,next to that number is the experience in that skill. but i only know that skill 1 is attack and 3 is hp :P, you’ll have to figure those out. Hope I helped.
